<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
  <title>Admin • E-mail test</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.css" />
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900 text-white p-4">
  <header class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
    <div><h1 class="text-xl font-bold">Admin • E-mail</h1></div>
    <nav class="flex gap-2">
      <a href="/calendar" class="bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-600 px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm shadow-sm">Kalendarz</a>
      <a href="/fill" class="bg-emerald-600 px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm hover:bg-emerald-500">Wypełnij okienka</a>
      <a href="/logout" class="bg-slate-700 px-3 py-2 rounded text-sm">Wyloguj</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-xl mx-auto rounded-xl border border-emerald-500/30 bg-slate-900/60 p-5 shadow-lg">
    <h2 class="font-semibold mb-4">Wyślij testowe powiadomienie e-mail (AWS SES)</h2>
    <p class="text-xs text-slate-300 mb-4">Upewnij się, że <code>EMAIL_FROM</code> i adresy odbiorców są zweryfikowane w SES (w trybie sandbox).</p>
    <form method="POST" action="/admin/email" class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm mb-1">Odbiorca</label>
        <select name="username" class="w-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded px-3 py-2">
          <option value="stefania">Stefania</option>
          <option value="jacek">Jacek</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm mb-1">Wiadomość (opcjonalnie)</label>
        <textarea name="custom" rows="4" class="w-full bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 rounded px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Własny tekst wiadomości... Jeśli puste, wyślemy domyślny komunikat z personalizacją."></textarea>
      </div>
      <button class="w-full bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 px-4 py-2 rounded font-semibold">Wyślij</button>
    </form>
    <% if (msg) { %>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-amber-200"><%= msg %></p>
    <% } %>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
